# Memo fresh install Rasp 

Stqrting with fresh install of raspb lite 


## NETWORKING 

By default wifi is blocked on fres install (http://www.geekmind.net/2011/01/linux-wifi-operation-not-possible-due.html#:~:text=Linux%20WiFi%3A%20operation%20not%20possible%20due%20to%20RF-kill,rfkill%27s%20soft%20and%20hard%20block%20from%20syncing%20correctly.)
```rfkill unblock wifi```

Wifi might be soft blocked to(https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/45338/iwlist-interface-doesnt-support-scanning-ubuntu-lts-10-04)

bring down/ mode managed / up 
```
sudo ifconfig wlan0 down
sudo iwconfig wlan0 mode Managed
sudo ifconfig wlan0 up
sudo iwlist wlan0 scan
```

To configure wpa suplicant(https://linuxconfig.org/how-to-connect-to-wifi-from-the-cli-on-debian-10-buster)

/!\ interface reseau par defaut : p2p-interfqce, l'enlever dans /var/run/wpa_supplicant/p2p...


